| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4745 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 801b0abd-73bd-5c2d-b19d-f54903d16e82"
